Package org.mxupdate.update

Class Summary
AbstractAdminObject_mxJPO The class is used to export, create, delete and update administration objects within MX.
AbstractObject_mxJPO Abstract class from which must be derived for exporting and importing all administration (business) objects.
AbstractPropertyObject_mxJPO  
BusObject_mxJPO The class is used to export, create, delete and update business objects within MX.
BusObject_mxJPO.AttributeValue Class used to hold the attributes values.
BusObject_mxJPO.Connection The class is used to store information about one connection including all attributes values and the type, name with revision of the connected business object.
